CT-HYB
------------------------------------------
Hybridization expansion quantum Monte Carlo impurity solver: An open-source
implementation of the continuous-time hybridization-expansion quantum Monte
Carlo method.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.3.5-1
  libalps2-2.2.0-1bl3
  libalpscore_cthyb-devel-1.0.3-1bl1
  libalpscore_cthyb1-1.0.3-1bl1
  libgcc1-11.3.0-1
  libopenmpi40-4.1.2-1
  libstdc++6-11.3.0-1
  pkg-config-1.8.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.38-1
  cmake-3.20.0-1
  cygport-0.35.1-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  gcc-g++-11.3.0-1
  libalps-devel-2.2.0-1bl3
  libopenmpi-devel-4.1.2-1
  ninja-1.11.0-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/ALPSCore/CT-HYB

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/ALPSCore/CT-HYB/archive/refs/tags/v1.0.3.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack CT-HYB-1.0.3-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./CT-HYB-1.0.3-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/CT-HYB-1.0.3-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/CT-HYB-1.0.3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libalpscore_cthyb1-1.0.3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libalpscore_cthyb-devel-1.0.3-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(CT-HYB)
  /usr/bin/hybmat.exe
  /usr/share/doc/CT-HYB/LICENSE.txt
  /usr/share/doc/CT-HYB/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/CT-HYB.README

(libalpscore_cthyb1)
  /usr/bin/cygalpscore_cthyb-1.dll

(libalpscore_cthyb-devel)
  /usr/include/alps/cthyb/solver.hpp
  /usr/lib/cmake/ALPSCoreCTHYB/alpscorecthyb-config-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/ALPSCoreCTHYB/alpscorecthyb-config.cmake
  /usr/lib/libalpscore_cthyb.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/CT-HYB.pc

